snippet.title: The most advanced self-learning solution for classes 6-12
snippet.description:
LearnNext is an interactive, computer-based self-learning solution which helps students retain concepts better and perfect them with exhaustive practice and tests. Through HD animated videos, practice papers and all-India tests, detailed performance reports and other exciting features, LearnNext helps students in achieving conceptual clarity and creating a strong academic base. 

To watch the complete lesson, register to get 5-day full access for free
visit - http://bit.ly/2KbImVd
